        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "As the sand which is on the sea-shore ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— An hyperbolical expression to signify a vast number. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Eating and drinking, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — In perfect security, and highly satisfied. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Jeshurun now ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "began to ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "wax fat, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "as Moses foresaw would be the case, and soon ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "kicked; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "soon ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "forsook God who made him, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "lightly esteemed the rock of his salvation, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 32:15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". This even Solomon himself did. What individual, or what nation, can bear continual prosperity and plenty?",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
