        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Many ... - See 1 Kings 3:8 note; and compare Psalm 127:1-5, which is traditionally ascribed to Solomon, and which celebrates the populousness and security of Israel in his day. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Many ... - See ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
